result.adr_address: 23 Staunton St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Awtar Restaurant

reviews.text:
The food is always great — shisha? depends who prepares it. 

you need to work on the new extension on the ground floor. Your staff provided really below average service. 

It was not a busy night in that section (started with 2 table of guests at around 8pm and around 5 tables at 10-11pm) 

Your staff was barely there to attend to 5 tables. The staff should be on the FLOOR not hiding in the kitchen. When I asked for a drinks menu, I had to walk all the way to the kitchen to get the staff’s attention only to find her using her mobile phone (I think she would prefer not be there at all — why bother?) 

We visited on the 12th July, a Friday night. 

I like the place, the food and I always recommend it but this time sadly the service could have been better. You would expect that investing in an extension on the ground floor, you would also invest in serving your guests there. It almost felt as if that was section was specifically built to seat unwanted guests. 

If they had simply paid attention to what was on the floor I wouldn’t be writing this review. Maybe your staff are overworked?
Shisha is great here as are the staff and food.
The place to get an ice pipe shisha and some yummy bites. Indoor and outdoor seating. Dog allowed. More awesome with a chatty crowd

Everything was nice so were the staffs but the sisha was not , I hope u could improve that cause the tst awtar has the best one so I thought here would be the same here but it isn't and it was dissapointing aswell
good food

海外初シーシャ。
料理も美味しいし、シーシャも美味しい。
行ったのは秋頃で丁度いい季候だった。
たまたま外の席が空いていたので外で吸ったが何時間でもいられそうな心地よさ。
客層は日本人はおらず、外国人（英語？を話してたと思う）が多い感じ。
燃えきった葉は捨てていくスタイル。自分が知ってるフレーバーは入れっぱなし、とは違った…。
そのおかげか最初のフレッシュな香りが長く続くような気がする。多分。
同じくらいの時期にまた行きたい。

Everything was nice so were the staffs but the sisha was not , I hope u could improve that cause the tst awtar has the best one so I thought here would be the same here but it isn't and it was dissapointing aswell
